(44, 'Ananta', 'Ananta Hotels & Resorts', 'Ananta', 'Udaipur', 'Rajasthan', 'Ananta Hotels and Resorts, luxury hotels and resorts in India that epitomizes in blissful settings. Our attentive staff is committed to providing you with service excellence, making our resorts an excellent choice for your next vacation.\n\nOur resorts are spread across acres of lush greenery, and each one offers a unique and unforgettable experience. Whether you\'re looking for a romantic getaway, a family vacation, or a business trip, we have a resort that\'s perfect for you.\n\nOur luxurious accommodations, our resorts also feature a variety of dining options, wellness facilities, and recreation activities. So whether you\'re looking to pamper your palate, relax in a spa, or explore the great outdoors, we have something for everyone.', 'https://www.anantahotels.com/', '/hotel-images/the-ananta-udaipur.avif', '2025-06-30 10:07:50', 'India'),
(45, 'Fariyas Resort', 'Fariyas Group of Hotels', NULL, 'Lonavala', NULL, NULL, 'https://www.fariyas.com/', '/hotel-images/fariyas-resort-lonavala.jpg', '2025-06-30 10:07:50', 'India'),
